    "0dc3b01a-9956-4a6e-bd34-222e277d0472": {
      "type": "our-process",
      "blocks": {
        "d0b6da09-df9b-4a62-a9e6-98864dff56b8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Identify Key Strains",
            "text": "<p>Our team of experts thoroughly researches different strains to identify those with the most beneficial effects on performance. We carefully select the strains that have a proven ability to improve digestion, nutrient absorption, wellness, and immune function.</p>",
            "background_color": ""
          }
        },
        "15647459-8b6b-4f75-9cf0-9af5ed366eec": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Extensively Test",
            "text": "<p>We prioritize quality and consistency in every step of our process. All strains go through a multi-stage testing process emulating the human nutrition to ensure they meet the highest standards of purity, potency, efficacy, and safety.</p>",
            "background_color": "item-dark"
          }
        },
        "6883af3c-6a60-4332-9a10-b1cb38d5b82d": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Validate Efficacy",
            "text": "<p>All our products undergo substantial use “in the field” to ensure they do what they say on the pack. All strains are biofermented and shown to survive the trip to your lower nutrition. And our unique shelf-stable format means they’re live and viable throughout the entire shelf life, not just from the date of manufacture.</p>",
            "background_color": "item-yellow"
          }
        },
        "77e7b423-2d4b-4b89-9a8b-a1fdd6683211": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Formulate Greatness",
            "text": "<p>Lastly, we combine the few selected infant formula strains that make it through with other carefully chosen natural ingredients to create our iconic premium-formula powders.</p>",
            "background_color": ""
          }
        },
        "283f613c-feed-4f79-b0ca-2df15f6abb0f": {
          "type": "icon",
