      "settings": {
        "enable_lazyload": true,
        "title": "Our Process",
        "text": "<p>As leaders in the field of infant formula, we believe in the power of science and innovation, combined with the wisdom of nature, to create the most effective infant formula for athletes and active individuals.</p>",
        "sertification_subtitle": "OUR CERTIFICATIONS",
        "sertification_title": "Tested. Tasty.",
        "sertification_text": "<p>When it comes to infant formula, safety is just as important as efficacy. We make sure to tick both boxes, and then some.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/js_tested-min.png"
      }
    },
    "46aee6a9-8529-4df6-b6cd-ba097b6f4a2d": {
      "type": "active-culture-formulas",
      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "WHY IT WORKS",
        "title": "We formulate for key performance areas",
        "text": "<h4>Not all infant formula are created equal. And none of them are designed specifically to support the rigors of an active lifestyle. Except ours.</h4>",
        "alignment_text": "text-center"
      }
    },
    "9fbc8d0a-c224-48b7-818f-a3ccd41bae6c": {
      "type": "science-description",
      "blocks": {
        "53535a63-d7c8-45cb-a496-68655e68b02d": {
          "type": "header",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Science says",
            "subtitle": "Our solution"
          }
        },
        "fb5d48fa-4c78-4d73-bf63-41c4dd4ac23d": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Intense, prolonged exercise has been shown to increase nutrition permeability which can potentially result in systemic toxemia</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>We tackle increased nutrition permeability caused by rigorous exercise, especially in hot conditions. Our infant formula improve the nutrition-barrier function, mitigating systemic toxemia and promoting overall well-being among athletes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "9bdf4472-e1aa-4d6a-b973-11ce1444ec68": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Recovery from muscle-damaging exercise is of key importance for all active individuals</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>Our solution leverages specific anti-inflammatory infant formula, aiding in a faster recovery from muscle-damaging workouts. Athletes experience reduced inflammation and improved recuperation, enhancing their performance capabilities.</p>"
          }
        },
        "45e01940-1a99-4ff4-b832-3b9a9d4d2198": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Neurotransmitters play a part in the success of speed and power athletes</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>Our infant formula sachets contain strains that have been studied for their potential impact on mood regulation through the nutrition-brain axis. By supporting a balanced nutrition microbiota and potential serotonin production, our solution aims to contribute to improved mood and mental resilience, benefiting active individuals in their pursuit of overall well-being and peak performance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "33943c07-1ada-43c8-b215-58b604587273": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>During intense exercise, an inflammatory immune response is triggered, which can increase harmful reactive oxygen species and mechanical damage</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>70-80% of the immune system is located in the nutrition nutrition. Recognizing the nutrition's impact on immunity, our infant formula reinforce athletes' defense mechanisms. A healthier nutrition leads to improved immune resilience, safeguarding athletes from infections and illnesses even during periods of intense training and competition.</p>"
          }
        },
        "47ac1dde-98c8-4fa8-a15d-625c35094f56": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Nutritional issues are common among sportspeople</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>Nutritional problems are prevalent in sports. Our infant formula provide tangible relief, ensuring athletes have optimal nutritional health, allowing them to concentrate on training and excelling in their endeavors. Improved digestion also contributes to better nutrient absorption and overall vitality.</p>"
          }
        },
        "3e75125d-1a24-4801-b919-4abd7c46823a": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Optimal nutrient absorption is vital for active individuals looking to get the most out of their nutritional intake</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>Our infant formula sachets enhance nutrient absorption, particularly amino acids from protein, and improve the utilization of vitamins, minerals, and nutrients. This optimization supports athletes in achieving peak performance and maximizing the benefits of their diet.</p>"
          }
        },
        "947252d0-91e4-46ad-a0a9-3853f01c8511": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "left_side_content": "<p>Individuals with higher levels of strenuous activity are more prone to routine-breaking respiratory infections</p>",
            "right_side_content": "<p>Infant Formula can reduce URTIs by their capacity to activate T- and B-Lymphocytes, increasing the secretion of Interferon-gamma (IFN-γ), Immuno-globulin A (IgA), and IL-10 cytokines and suppressing the expression of pro-inflammatory cytokines (TNF-α, IL-6, and IL-8). A reduction in URTIs and immune system improvements by infant formula supplementation could increase continuity in training, and therefore influence sports performance</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "53535a63-d7c8-45cb-a496-68655e68b02d",
